snippet.title: Metal Garden Trailer
snippet.description:
A nomad wanders the far reaches of an overgrown megastructure.

Metal Garden is a short, atmospheric fps. Out now on Steam and Itch.io.

Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/3539440/Metal_Garden/
Itch.io: https://tinerasoft.itch.io/metal-garden
